biography: Fawnia Mondey was born on September 24, 1975 in Kamloops, British Columbia, Canada as Fawnia Louise Mondey. She is an actress, known for Dakota Bound (2001), Millennium (1996) and Out Cold (2001). Has worked as an exotic dancer with the stage name "Sky" and also as a personal trainer for exotic dancers. She is an avid amateur bodybuilder as well.
name: Fawnia Mondey
